verses.1: Israel uliante hih bangin tamlawh in hong ci hi:
verses.2: Na nu uh humpinelkai tawh kibang hi. Humpinelkai dangte tawh kikhawlin, a note a khoi hi.
verses.3: A note khat thuhilh a, hong khang cing hi. Sabet zong hong siam a, mi hong ne hi.
verses.4: Mite in tua thu za uh a, gum sungah awksak uh hi. Bawm sungah khum uh a, Egypt gamah paipih uh hi.
verses.5: A pi º lametna teng bei ta hi. A no dang khat pantah leuleu a, a khang cing khat a suah hi.
verses.6: Amah hong khang cing a, a dangte tawh kikhawl hi. Sabet zong hong siam a, mi hong ne hi.
verses.7: Kulhpite su gawp a, khuapite siasak hi. Hawk zelzel a, a za mite lau mahmah hi.
verses.8: Amah a hih dingin mite kikaikhawm uh a, mun khempeuh panin hong kuan uh hi. A ngenthang uh zak uh a, thang ah a awksak uh hi.
verses.9: Bawm sungah khum uh a, Babylon kumpipa kiang a tunpih uh hi. Israel mual tung tengah ama hawkna a kizak nawn loh nadingin a khumcip uh hi.
verses.10: Na nu uh, luitui gei ah a kisuan leenggui tawh kibang hi. Tui tampi ngah a, a teh, a gah, a pha hi.
verses.11: A gui hiangte hong lian a, kumpi ciangkhut hong suak hi. Leenggui hong khang a, van hong ban hi. A teh pha-in sang mahmah a, mi khempeuh in mu kim hi.
verses.12: Ahi zongin hehna tawh leenggui kizung bawh a, leilak kidenna hi. Nisuahna huihpi hong nung a, a gah teeng keu tumsak hi. A hiangte kikuai tan a, keu-in kihal tum hi.
verses.13: Tui om lohna lei keu gamah tu-in hih leenggui kituah hi.
verses.14: Hih leenggui mei in kaang a, a hiang a gah kaang tum mang hi. A hiangte liankik nawn lo dinga, kumpi ciangkhut suakkik ngei nawn lo ding hi. Hih a tunga pen tamlawhna hi a, a kisa zelzel ngei khat ahi hi.
